{"tid":2135702,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"將軍澳醫院一名確診者企圖逃離醫院 準備搭的士前遭截獲","createTime":"2020-08-01T15:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T03:48:54.000Z","uid":212626,"like":354,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"e33adb0040801d722d421bac405340c685b22893","tid":2135702,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:24:12.000Z","msg":"警方晚上7時許接報，將軍澳醫院一名感染新型冠狀病毒的58歲陳姓男子企圖離開醫院，聲稱要返回新蒲崗辦公室收拾財物。醫院職員見狀報警，警方到場在醫院門外截獲該名病人，他當時正準備上的士離開，警方其後把病人交回醫院處理。本報正向醫管局查詢。<br />\n<br />\n西貢區議員馮君安表示，收到相關消息，稱涉事男子不適到醫院檢查，接受快速測試後確診，懷疑因「太驚」而逃離醫院，促請院方或警方公布該病人逃走後有否到過哪些地方。馮君安指出，醫院門口到的士站有200米距離，擔心途中病人接觸到的人會有受感染風險。"},{"pid":"8b8444eb883095a26820258d762db1b573d8a8a1","tid":2135702,"uid":66324,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:25:39.000Z","msg":"link?"},{"pid":"6fd801ea087fc7588825ec728a8cfa132fdb96ee","tid":2135702,"uid":187957,"like":398,"dislike":13,"score":385,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:25:44.000Z","msg":"呢D人不如直接火化"},{"pid":"bf5c6ff8dca0cbf09c3dc65a85b00a8fb4ad77e9","tid":2135702,"uid":212626,"like":15,"dislike":6,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"8b8444eb883095a26820258d762db1b573d8a8a1","tid":2135702,"uid":66324,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:25:39.000Z","msg":"link?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:26:31.000Z","msg":"日月報唔po link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea9de76d2b3e34b31eef15111bff09d7f1e850f","tid":2135702,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fd801ea087fc7588825ec728a8cfa132fdb96ee","tid":2135702,"uid":187957,"like":398,"dislike":13,"score":385,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:25:44.000Z","msg":"呢D人不如直接火化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87822d09c3a19a809d5e5517cba1e024a164cd2","tid":2135702,"uid":104138,"like":71,"dislike":0,