2020-08-01T15:47:32.000Z","msg":"樓主可唔可以同我做愛？<br />\n搵埋Sara一齊3p"},{"pid":"a9e4dfb0efb2d73c7183be49c1a23b84cc82ec61","tid":2135702,"uid":238214,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:47:54.000Z","msg":"自己知道確診. 係咪可以選擇不接受治療?<br />\n香港法律冇寫病者一定要強制接受醫治."},{"pid":"0dc98ecb05a5aa8956087faa09f07d9b9a121f89","tid":2135702,"uid":18547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:49:30.000Z","msg":"咪撚醫佢啦<br />\n掉佢上深圳算"},{"pid":"342a75bd3fc2c1aaec6fce9232ce62f5aae49a45","tid":2135702,"uid":238214,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:49:36.000Z","msg":"醫療程序：徵求同意與拒絕治療<br />\n<br />\nI. 徵求同意<br />\n一般來說，醫生如未取得病人同意，是不能為病人施予治療或展開醫療程序的。而病人接受的治療亦必須是他/她事前所同意接受的同一項治療。<br />\n<br />\n一旦病人沒有清晰表示同意，或完全同意在治療過程中讓醫生觸碰身體，任何涉及接觸病人身體的治療或療程會成為表面證供（prima facie），視作侵權或襲擊。即使醫生相信他/她的作為符合病人的最佳利益，或醫生的作為的確符合病人的最佳利益，表面證供仍然成立。<br />\n<br />\n香港醫務委員會為本港的註冊醫生制訂了《香港註冊醫生專業守則》（《守則》）。《守則》第II部分（醫務委員會於2015年12月發出的第二十二期會員通訊公布修訂《守則》第II部分）提及「徵求同意」：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/Medical_treatment_consent_and_withdrawal/all.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2FMedical_treatment_consent_and_withdrawal%2Fall.shtml&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62Plm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=3af07692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/Medical_treatment_consent_and_withdrawal/all.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"300aa00db122f61ed23a2c395aa3a0008c79a727","tid":2135702,"uid":158889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:49:58.000Z","msg":"做得好 最支持攬炒師"},{"pid":"dafcd67b0d569023f53afe0fc5da86d69ce8594a","tid":2135702,"uid":185712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3030da902c306ecbdc68ea18195bd5ab333e56c1","tid":2135702,"uid":66346,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"008fd97d33b2b196e06f063c54b9b59aa0331033","tid":2135702,"uid":29514,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e87822d09c3a19a809d5e5517cba1