序的。而病人接受的治療亦必須是他/她事前所同意接受的同一項治療。<br />\n<br />\n一旦病人沒有清晰表示同意，或完全同意在治療過程中讓醫生觸碰身體，任何涉及接觸病人身體的治療或療程會成為表面證供（prima facie），視作侵權或襲擊。即使醫生相信他/她的作為符合病人的最佳利益，或醫生的作為的確符合病人的最佳利益，表面證供仍然成立。<br />\n<br />\n香港醫務委員會為本港的註冊醫生制訂了《香港註冊醫生專業守則》（《守則》）。《守則》第II部分（醫務委員會於2015年12月發出的第二十二期會員通訊公布修訂《守則》第II部分）提及「徵求同意」：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/Medical_treatment_consent_and_withdrawal/all.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2FMedical_treatment_consent_and_withdrawal%2Fall.shtml&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62Plm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=3af07692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/Medical_treatment_consent_and_withdrawal/all.shtml</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T16:40:53.000Z","msg":"確診者就唔適用了<br />\n因為有傳染病條例強制留院"},{"pid":"1ea3bfb9270331ea2c6af685f40ba3282380e922","tid":2135702,"uid":94591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T16:41:01.000Z","msg":"笑乜撚<br />\n<br />\n分分鐘佢都手足 想走佬都係驚比港共抽dna"},{"pid":"419a94b6c4c91f538ca06bb94e0615a14491a7ca","tid":2135702,"uid":204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20454a30e261a8751a605c250b65e75712c1eacc","tid":2135702,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1c9bf423ac96641c40c3b90ee2c43dfe966e0d09","tid":2135702,"uid":6352,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a9e4dfb0efb2d73c7183be49c1a23b84cc82ec61","tid":2135702,"uid":238214,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:47:54.000Z","msg":"自己知道確診. 係咪可以選擇不接受治療?<br />\n香港法律冇寫病者一定要強制接受醫治."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:50:40.000Z","msg":"好似有法例寫明傳染病，因公眾利益，一定要接受治療"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T16:13:32.000Z","msg":"好似只限幾隻病先係<br />\n好似霍亂果D先得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T16:41:29.000Z","msg":"今次呢單武肺係on list"},{"pid":"7493b09a88de00b1f3b9d263c5956fbe32287824","tid":2135702,"uid":197716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ea29550d2c2d861e42e94ea2a639901110ce445","tid":2